            <title>[FLINK-5190] ZooKeeperLeaderRetrievalService should not close the zk client when stop</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-5190</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The zk client is created outside of ZooKeeperLeaderRetrievalService and psssed to it, when ZooKeeperLeaderRetrievalService stop, it should not stop the zk client as other may be using it outside.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
