&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/2905&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/2905&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-5190&quot; title=&quot;ZooKeeperLeaderRetrievalService should not close the zk client when stop&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLINK-5190&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLINK-5190&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;runtime&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; fix ZooKeeperLeaderRetrievalService close the &#8230;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    This pr is for jira #&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;5190&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-5190&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-5190&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    The zk client for ZooKeeperLeaderRetrievalService is pass from outside, if closing the zk client when stop, will influence others who want to use the zk client.&lt;/p&gt;

